:"text","value":"\n• 📍 地址：浙江省嘉興市桐鄉市烏鎮西柵景區內"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n• 📞 電話：+86 573-8873-1088"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n• 🌐 網址："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"http://www.wuzhen.com.cn/"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"烏鎮官網"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n• ✨ 特色：國際互聯網大會習近平宴請俄羅斯總理的指定餐廳, 以 烏鎮當地農家菜 為主，口味清淡健康"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"v025-02.jpeg","src":"/images/travel/v025-02.jpeg"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"2️⃣ 烏鎮民國時代"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n• 📍 地址：浙江省嘉興市桐鄉市烏鎮西柵景區內"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n• 📞 電話：+86"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n• 🌐 網址："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"http://www.wuzhen.com.cn/web/food/details?id=42/"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"烏鎮官網"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n• ✨ 特色：\n民国时代特色主题餐厅，是一座有百年历史的老宅子，有着石库拱门、花窗木格、琉璃灯、打字机、留声机等种种陈设........墙上投影播放着 30 年代的经典老电影，楼道、庭院回响着民国时期的名曲。餐厅包厢都以民国时期的文化名人来命名：志摩、爱玲、达夫、评梅，每个包厢还有遥相呼应的名人照片，来烘托环境氛围！"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"v025-04.jpeg","src":"/images/travel/v025-04.jpeg"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"2️⃣ 烏鎮通安中餐厅（何家小馆）"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n• 📍 地址：浙江省嘉興市桐鄉市烏鎮西柵景區內"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n• 📞 電話：+86 573-8873-1088"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n• 🌐 網址："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"http://www.wuzhen.com.cn/web/food/details?id=38"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"烏鎮官網"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n• ✨ 特色：餐厅门面是非常典型、精致的徽派砖雕门楼，上面刻有“翰墨千秋”四个大字，乌镇本是文人墨客的聚集地，茅盾诞生于此地。门内酒店内的中餐厅，映入眼帘的是一个红色大食盒，古时的士绅名流，出门访友，以至于把酒言欢，常会先准备一些菜肴果品，放在食盒内，作为助兴的下酒菜。餐厅内也放置了不同款式的食盒作为装饰。中餐厅餐位总共 434 个，下设 10 处别致高雅的包厢，所有包厢的名字都依托于一个“通”字，如通望、通达等，寓意着财运亨通、一帆风顺。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"v025-05.jpeg","src":"/images/travel/v025-05.jpeg"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"杭州"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"3️⃣ 山外山魚頭宴"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n• 📍 地址：杭州市西湖区玉泉路 8 号（植物园内玉泉景区旁）\n• 📞 電話：+86 571-8799-5866"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n• 🌐 網址："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.shanwaishan.com/"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"山外山官網"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n• ✨ 特色：山外山菜馆以追求自然品质为特色，积极推广杭州传统名菜系列，并首创千岛湖有机鱼系列，其中精品“八宝鱼头皇”最受顾客欢迎，享誉“杭城第一家”"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"v025-06.jpeg","src":"/images/travel/v025-06.jpeg"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"4️⃣ 知味觀·味莊"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n• 📍 地址：杭州市上城區楊公堤 10-12 號"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n• 📞 電話：+86 571-8797-8859"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n• 🌐 網址："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":""},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"知味觀官